data.description: New & Improved Pricing on this hidden gem! Welcome to 350 Andrew Dr. This 4 bedroom 2 bathroom home offers over 1700 sqft of living space and is ideal for those seeking a cozy home with ample space for the whole family. Built in 2006, this home is a true gem. The spacious bedrooms provide comfort and privacy for all family members. Primary bedroom is located on the main floor with an ensuite bathroom and walk in closet. Upstairs you will find 3 generous size bedrooms with a full bathroom. Home does feature a fireplace, vaulted ceilings, separate utility room, 2 car garage, fenced in back yard, and is in a well established neighborhood close to schools, shopping, and dining.
